data.description: Immaculate like-new Franklin Brothers Craftsman home located in the popular Mirada neighborhood in NE Bend offers move-in ready finishes throughout! Corner lot adds privacy. Custom wood shutter blinds, luxury vinyl flooring, gourmet kitchen island with SS appliances, Quartz countertops throughout the home, open floor plan, high ceilings, large primary suite with French doors, tiled shower and soaking tub, fully fenced yard with gorgeous landscaping. All bedrooms and two full bathrooms are on the second level. Mirada includes fun outdoor amenities like a pool, playground, pavilion and trails throughout Eagle Park. HOA also includes front yard landscaping and annual sprinkler blowout service. $270/quarterly. Home is prewired with sensors and control box for alarm service. Storage shed in back yard matches the homes colors.
